{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"308f710384","title":"学生中的右派言论","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a762b4a361","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"308f710384"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"286b355710","name":"高平原"},{"id":"6e84ff3b7b","name":"魏国平"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"bb0b806b4f","name":"陈月宦"},{"id":"e2d04ecf58","name":"涂必诚"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e2effd882a","type":"title","text":"学生中的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"0bc8d7795c","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院陈月宦魏国平高平原涂必诚","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"f85585e98e","type":"paragraph","text":"陈月宦说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"ced91813e3","type":"paragraph","text":"“汇报者是便衣警察，积极同学是笑面虎”。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"d42d205165","type":"paragraph","text":"魏国平说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"0b5fefd517","type":"paragraph","text":"“我又不是特务，为什么要汇报？”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"b92362099e","type":"paragraph","text":"高平原说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"ccc820ade7","type":"paragraph","text":"“向组织汇报是可耻的行为，弄成教研室的阴谋集团”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"e507e6dfb7","type":"paragraph","text":"他漫骂党员“是用打击别人、以取得上级的欢心，象警察一样培养一批爪牙，丧尽天良，对群众就象特务丁人一样。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"cdcb48d2df","type":"paragraph","text":"涂必诚说：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"},{"id":"d2d05475d2","type":"paragraph","text":"“我知道了组织性纪律性了，说的好的人，不一定作的好，前阶段我吃亏了，生活教育了我，知道以后怎么工作好，以后我加强汇报就是了。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384"}],"page":{"id":"d977d69ff1","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"308f710384","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}